    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-01-08T13:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-01-08T13:00:00-05:00" n="500"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d500">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/11–948: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-01-08T13:00:00-05:00"
                            >January 8, 1949—1 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>29. Dept desires supplemental report losses suffered by ChiGovt subsequent to
                    losses reported Embtel 2142 Nov 9.<note n="8" xml:id="d500fn8">
                        <ref target="frus1948v08#pg_196">
                            <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1948, vol. <hi
                                rend="smallcaps">viii</hi>, p. 196</ref>.</note> Request Emb
                    periodically forward such report providing info as requested Deptel 1527 Nov
                        2.<note n="9" xml:id="d500fn9">
                        <ref target="frus1948v08#pg_185">
                            <hi rend="italic">Ibid.</hi>, p. 185</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lovett</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
